acing="0" role="presentation" style="padding-bottom:32px;text-align:center"><tbody><tr><td><img alt="YNOT London" height="36" src="https://staging.ynotlondon.com/brand/ynot-logo-black.png" style="display:inline-block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none;height:auto;max-width:140px" width="140"/></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 style="font-family:Playfair Display, Georgia, serif;font-size:22px">Your prepaid return label is attached.</h2><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px">Hi Anna, your return RT-2026-00007 (from order YN-2026-00042) is approved. We&#x27;ve attached a prepaid Royal Mail label to this email.</p><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin-top:24px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:24px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#666;margin:0 0 8px;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0">Items in this return</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:4px 0;margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0">Coat × 1</p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:#e5e5e5;margin:24px 0"/><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:24px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#666;margin:0 0 8px;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0">Steps</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:4px 0;margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0">1. Print the attached PDF label.</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:4px 0;margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0">2. Pack the items securely with all original tags attached.</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:4px 0;margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0">3. Drop the parcel at any post office or postbox before 2026-05-15.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin-top:24px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:24px;margin:0;color:#666;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Please ship by 2026-05-15. If we don&#x27;t receive your return within 14 days we may not be able to process the refund.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:#e5e5e5;margin:48px 0 24px"/><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">YNOT London · 13 Elvaston Place, Flat 1, London SW7 5QG ·<!-- --> <a href="https://staging.ynotlondon.com" style="color:#666666">staging.ynotlondon.com</a></p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><!--/$--></body></html>"`;
